 GET /hotels

- Результат:
{ "hotels": [ { "id": 1, "name": "Hotel A", "city": "City 1", "country": "Country 1", "info": "Description of hotel A"},{ "id": 2, "name": "Hotel B", "city": "City 2", "country": "Country 1", "info": "Description of hotel B"}]

- Получить отель по его ID:
  Запрос: GET /hotels/:id

- Результат:
{ "id": 1, "name": "Hotel A", "city": "City 1", "country": "Country 1", "description": "Description of hotel A"}
